I wanted to follow up on the project timeline we discussed. The initial draft is nearly ready for review, and I think we should schedule a brief check-in next week to align on the next steps. Could you send over your availability for Tuesday or Wednesday afternoon? I'll bring the updated documents to that meeting. Also, don't forget to bring the sample materials we talked about last time. Let me know if you need me to coordinate with anyone else from the design team beforehand.

COSTCO WHOLESALE

Your Annual Perks Are Updated

An invitation for current Costco Members.

As a valued Costco Wholesale member in a participating location, you are invited to share your opinions. Your participation helps us serve you better. In appreciation, eligible members may receive the following items, with no payment required:

A Keurig Coffee Maker for the first 2,000 qualifying participants.

A 12-month membership term provided at no charge to eligible participants.

Availability is based on the number of participants.

Start Your Questionnaire Participation

What We Value

Member Feedback

Your insights directly influence warehouse offerings and services.

Program Details

The questionnaire is brief and designed for existing Costco members.

Thank you for your time and for being a Costco Wholesale member. We appreciate your continued partnership.

Regarding the weekend plans, yes, I think arriving around 10 am should work perfectly. I'll bring the hiking gear and some snacks for the trail. Did you check the weather forecast? It looks like it might be a bit chilly in the morning, so maybe pack an extra layer. Also, let me know if you want to carpool from the usual spot. I can pick you up if that's easier. We should probably decide on which trailhead to use before we go.

